{{!--
  doclet.hbs - Default/fallback page template.

  This is the base template for most doclet kinds (class, namespace, mixin, etc.).
  It extends site/layout without overriding any blocks, which means it inherits
  the full default layout: page header, breadcrumbs, access filter, primary symbol
  section, and secondary symbol sections (via the symbol-kinds helper).

  Kind-specific templates (module.hbs, readme.hbs, source.hbs, tutorial.hbs, list.hbs)
  override specific blocks when they need custom rendering.

  Template resolution: handlebarsHelper.render() checks for tmpl[doclet.kind] first,
  then falls back to this template (tmpl.doclet).
--}}
